## \_removeByIdentifier() function

Remove an object from an array of objects

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export declare function _removeByIdentifier<T>(originals: Maybe<ImmutableArray<T>>, deletedId: ImmutableArray<unknown>, identifier: Prop<Immutable<T>>): Immutable<T>[];
```

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  originals | Maybe&lt;ImmutableArray&lt;T&gt;&gt; | An array of objects |
|  deletedId | ImmutableArray&lt;unknown&gt; | A unique value used to find the object to delete |
|  identifier | Prop&lt;Immutable&lt;T&gt;&gt; | A property on the object that contains the unique value |
